// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-2223 — Mass File Rename (mindware)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: a23427bf-f419-5510-bd84-7794ddb044bd

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
